                </cmdsynopsis>
        </refsynopsisdiv>

        <refsect1>
                <title>Description</title>

                <para><command>youtube_dlhelper</command> helps by downloading Music from Youtube.
                        You are running the program inside the command line with a Youtube URL. Then it
                        asks for a group name or interpreters name. Now it creates a Subfolder inside
                        your Musicdirectory. Then it makes a OGG or MP3 from the downloaded file and moves it
                        to the folder.</para>
        </refsect1>

